            "body": "@tris203 \r\n\r\n> A server capability equal to the method means there is no related server capability.\r\n\r\nsounds like a useful comment to add to the code...\r\n\r\n> it would be better if this could be tested and caught upstream before releasing.\r\n\r\nsure, we apparently are missing test coverage for this. tests live here: \r\n\r\n    make functionaltest TEST_FILE=test/functional/plugin/lsp_spec.lua\r\n\r\n",
